COACH.estimation_method.AverageOfTwo.AverageOfTwo module¶

Example estimation method that takes two parameters and returns the average of them.

class COACH.estimation_method.AverageOfTwo.AverageOfTwo.AverageOfTwo[source]¶

Bases: COACH.framework.coach.EstimationMethod

This is a simple example of an estimation method. It takes two parameters, X and Y, and the result is the average of them.
